# Data source for the report
The data used in this report come from the [Local Data Bank (BDL)](https://bdl.stat.gov.pl/bdl/start) at Statistics Poland. They were downloaded from the Local Data Bank website using the `bdl` package and concern the median price per 1 m^2^ of residential premises sold in market transactions in Wielkopolskie Voivodeship in the years 2010 - 2024. The data cover both the primary and secondary markets. It should be emphasized that Statistics Poland’s data on the price per square meter are widely used in analytical reports and industry publications (cf. e.g. @golkabeska2024rynek).


